{"lang": "zh_CN", "eventid": "act50side", "eventName": "泡影苍霆", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "TD-5", "avgTag": "行动后", "storyName": "只能成功，不能失败", "storyInfo": "月见夜的计划成功，大部分野兽被坑杀，但月见夜却因此落单。而等空爆赶到时，只看到“雷之主”和倒下的月见夜......", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g4_bambooforest", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冷风穿过竹叶，发出呜咽般的声响，如同亡魂的低语。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$leaveshake", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一支三十人的精锐部队，正用特制的绞索和滚木，拖动着“异兽”熔火蜗那小山般的尸体，在林间艰难行进。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尸体上，黑色的“诅咒”气息如活物般缓缓蠕动，散发出硫磺混着腐肉般的甜腥气味。周围的竹子一染上这股气息，便迅速变黑。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#10$2", "focus": "m", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这黑气看来真的能影响环境，真奇怪。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#10$2"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“诅咒”究竟是什么，月见夜？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#10$2"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有许多人研究过“诅咒”，但是，没有人得出过肯定的结论。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们只知道，人一旦接近“诅咒”太久，或者吃下了被“诅咒”的野兽的肉，也会受到“诅咒”影响，然后离奇死去。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而如果有地方被“诅咒”侵染太久，也会变得十分诡异，难以接近。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在泡影国东边，就有一片竹林，百年前，曾有一头“异兽”身上的“诅咒”在那里爆发，直到今天，那片竹林依然是禁地。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#6$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......真亏你们能在这种地方生活到今天。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#10$2"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自然虽然对我们多有考验，但也对我们多有馈赠，这很公平。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我喜欢，比想着我要尊重动物，我要尊重植物，哎呀，狩猎真野蛮之类的想法要强。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是指梓兰小姐？", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#4$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可没这么说，是你说的。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#14$2"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢，你喜欢狩猎吗，空爆小姐？", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我？我......不知道。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#13$2"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2106_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "将军！许多野兽把我们包围了！", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2106_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和计划一样！", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要回头！不要恋战！保持速度，目标地点就在前方两里处！", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$leaveshake"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2112_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2112_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$frontline_intro", "key": "$frontline_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "月见夜，你们先赶路，这里交给我吧。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#2$2"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你确定？", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虽然我不知道我喜不喜欢狩猎，但是，我肯定很喜欢这把新武器！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "别妨碍我！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道了。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尝尝这个！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_caxe_attack1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key"