了！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#4$2"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "别高兴得太早，空爆小姐。清点伤亡，然后——", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "将军！我们脚下！我们脚下这块高地也在裂开！", "name": "武士B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是吧？！这里也要塌了？！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好！塌陷范围超过了预期！快撤！", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#2$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "loop": "false", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一块巨大的岩石从他们身边滚落，将队伍冲散。"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "混乱中，空爆和义经被岩石推向了一边，而月见夜为了保护几名险些坠落的武士，被另一波塌陷的土石隔绝开来，与大部队失去了联系。"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g1_impermanence_street", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不必跟着吾，也不用担心吾，吾答应了月见夜，自然会做到。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信你。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是......有点担心你。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不必担心。这次“试炼”，是吾的“试炼”。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你们是被“御轮”送到这里的，泡影国本就对你们有所亏欠。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "现在，“异兽”已经被狩猎，“御轮”却出事，你们无法回家，吾更是无颜面对你们。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这些都是吾必须扛起的责任。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你把自己绷得太紧了，宝巫迦。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“御轮”的问题显然也不出在你身上，泡影国也好，你也好，你们都不亏欠我们什么。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "谢谢你的好意，梓兰小姐。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，无论如何，对你来说，回到家园是头等大事吧？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......没错。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾一定会找到将你们送回去的方法。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是想来催促你，只是——", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是因为你的身边有一个和吾长得一样的孩子吗？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你为什么会......", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一次见面的时候，你们对吾的态度，还有“泡普卡”这个名字，吾就有所猜测了。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一定很关心那个孩子，所以才会这么关心吾。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......也不是这个原因。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也许一开始是，但现在也不是了。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那么，为什么？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "关心他人是理所当然的事情。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但吾不需要。吾说过了，吾可以独自解决这些问题，吾做得到。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你和月见夜一样，也在内心深处认为吾做不到，对吗？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......如果是别人这么说，我确实会以为她在逞强，但是，我知道你做得到。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那为什么——", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在某种程度上，我理解月见夜的想法。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或许，他并不是害怕你做不到，他怕的是你做得到。 ", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 4.0, "ystrength": 4.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 30.0, "fadeout": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都城里，所有人都被远处竹林传来的巨大声响和冲天烟尘所震撼。"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2106_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成功了！月见夜将军成功了！东边的兽潮......消失了！", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2106_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那家伙确实有两下子。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他总是这样......把所有危险都揽在自己身上。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "听起来，你们本该是最亲密的伙伴，为什么会变成现在这样，总是针锋相对？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "母亲政务繁忙......是他一直在吾身边。教吾战斗，陪吾读书。母亲失踪，吾刚刚继位的时候，也是他替吾承担了那些最麻烦的事务。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾感谢他，但是吾无法忍受每次提及“雷之主”时，他的那种目光。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他从未真正限制吾的行动，但他的目光却像是在告诉吾——“你去做吧，等你失败的时候，你会知道的。”", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......月见夜确实也有他的问题。这样吧，等他回来之后，我们一起吃顿饭。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好好聊一聊“雷之主”的事，如何？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g4_bambooforest", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "月见夜呢？月见夜在哪？！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2106_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "将军为了救我们，被......被塌方带到另一边去了！", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2106_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_skillroar_hyper", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然，她听到远处传来一声熟悉的、充满王者威严的咆哮，不禁一怔。那声音穿透了尘埃与轰鸣，直击她的灵魂。"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这个声音......难道说——“雷之主”？！它怎么会在这里？！糟了！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "义经，我们走！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#8$2"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$5", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_dog_voice1"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（焦急的吼叫）", "name": "义经"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$5"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（那是......月见夜手下的武士？全都倒下了......周围这些野兽的尸体......这里到底发生了什么？）", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（月见夜？！）", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（他怎么会......伤得这么重！铠甲都碎了......连刀都断了......喂喂，开玩笑的吧，你可别死啊！）", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#12$2"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "月见夜！你撑住！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#12$2"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（糟了！动不了了！这股气息......是从哪里来的？！好可怕的压迫感......身体完全不听使唤了......）", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#12$2"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（头......只能勉强抬起来......）", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#12$2"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_dog_voice1"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（愤怒的吼叫）", "name": "义经"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（那是......“雷之主”？！）", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（它的样子......好奇怪......）", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（那些黑色的雾气......是“诅咒”吧？从那些野兽尸体上冒出来的......）", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（等等，“雷之主”身上发光了？那是什么？白色的光......）", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（这个光......我见过！和宝巫迦跳舞的时候一模一样！怎么可能？！）", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（它......它在吸收那些黑气！用宝巫迦的力量？！）", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（为什么？！为什么这头野兽会用宝巫迦她们家族代代相传的神圣力量？！难道说......）", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在吸收完所有“诅咒”之后，“雷之主”似乎心满意足。"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它低下头，冰冷的兽瞳瞥了一眼地上的月见夜，随即仰天发出一声震耳欲聋的咆哮。"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_skillroar_hyper", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那咆哮中，似乎充满了无尽的威严与......胜利的宣告。"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}